				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Personally, I see it as one person's bitch-and-whine-fest because this one change will effect him/her personally.  I see this thread as being totally self-centered on the part of the author.  
<br />

<br />
There is no way an upgrade to these 2 spells would be able to benefit all magicians.  There simply isn't enough room in BoT to allow more than just a handful of mages running around charming and mezzing mobs.  Calling for an upgrade to a couple of spells that would benefit such a small minority of players is just crazy.  Yet when the person who admittedly has benefited by using these 2 spells to monopolize a single zone in order to raise platinum and AA's turns out to be the one yelling the loudest about the lack of upgrades, it just points out the personal bias guiding the author's thought process and reasoning.
<br />

<br />
Give us new spells or upgrades to spells that will benefit ALL mages, not just the couple of mages that have given up on progression (sorry, but BoT is not high end/end game) in order to camp BoT named mobs in order to sell ornate drops for their personal gain.
<br />

<br />
